Author: steinsg8#0288
Content: What are the dangers of blockchain game platforms? Aren't they more susceptible to cheating since value is attached? Bots would be a big issue I think. Any advantages or disadvantages to current centralized systems?

Author: jl777c#5810
Content: less cheating as the blockchain can guarantee the game was actually played and not just that someone tweaked some files in the centralized DB

Author: jl777c#5810
Content: any bots that work on the decentralized version would also work on the centralized, so both share that same issue

Author: jl777c#5810
Content: it isnt any specific disadvantage of blockchain games, just something all games have

Author: jl777c#5810
Content: disadvantage would be that blockchain games will be slower for the operations as compared to a centralized DB.

Author: steinsg8#0288
Content: Hmmm, thank you.
